	//Why Choose Us
	section.section.section-xl.bg-default.text-center
		.container
			.title-10.wow.fadeInDown Select your Package
			.divider
			h4.title-11.wow.fadeInUp We provide a variety of pricing options so that you could select what
				br.d-none.d-lg-block
				|  you want for your fitness needs and goals.
			.row.row-xl.row-30.row-lg-50
